value":"false"},{"id":"ReferenciaDeLujo","type":"FLAG","value":"false"},{"id":"ReferenciaMadre","type":"FLAG","value":"false"},{"id":"VentaSinStock","type":"FLAG","value":"false"},{"id":"SenyalInternet","type":"FLAG","value":"false"},{"id":"SenyalInternetCodificacion","type":"FLAG","value":"true"}]},{"id":"ProveedorMarca","type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"NumeroProveedor","type":"STRING","value":"0000677"},{"id":"NombreProveedor","type":"STRING","value":"VENDRELL GOURMET, S.L."},{"id":"Fabricante","type":"STRING","value":"0000677"},{"id":"DescripcionFabricante","type":"STRING","value":"JOSé MIGUEL VENDRELL GUILLEM"},{"id":"Marca","type":"STRING","value":"GENESIS"},{"id":"MarcaMostradaEnWeb","type":"RELATIONSHIP","groupID":"391","id_Ext":"8108305056","value":"GENESIS"}]},{"id":"DescripcionCorta","type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"DescripcionTicket","type":"STRING","value":"CERVEZA ARTES"}]},{"id":"DescripcionLargaDelProducto","ocurrence":0,"type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"DescripcionPrincipal","type":"STRING","children":[{"id":"es_ES","ocurrence":0,"type":"STRING","value":"Génesis Toronja mezcla l atradición y vanguardia. El clasicismo proviene de su elaboración artesanal (sin conservantes y colorantes); la novedad de incorporar naranja."},{"id":"es_ES","ocurrence":1,"type":"STRING","value":"Mezcla perfecta de agua, malta, lúpulos y naranjas valencianas, las cuales, proceden de huertos propios y corresponden a la marca Vendrell Gourmet. De color anaranjado con cierta turbidez y la espuma es blanca y ligera. En nariz manda el aroma a cereal y las notas profundas a cítricos que aporta la naranja. En boca se presenta con una entrada fácil y un carbónico muy integrado y cremoso que hace que le paso sea aterciopelado. Todo construye una acidez equilibraa que da frescura confiriendo un final de boca cítrico en el que reaparece la fruta."},{"id":"en_GB","ocurrence":0,"type":"STRING","value":"Génesis Toronja combines the traditional with the cutting edge. Classicism comes from its artisanal production (without preservatives or colouring); the new idea of incorporating orange."},{"id":"en_GB","ocurrence":1,"type":"STRING","value":"The perfect mix of water, malt, hops and Valencia oranges, which come from the company's orchards and are from the brand Vendrell Gourmet. A cloudy orange colour with a light, white head. A bouquet of an aroma of grains and deep notes of citrus fruits brought out by the orange. Easy to drink, with a very integrated and creamy carbonation which turns velvety in the mouth. This builds a balanced acidity full of freshness, giving a citric, fruity aftertaste."},{"id":"fr_FR","ocurrence":0,"type":"STRING","value":"Génesis Toronja mêle la tradition et l'avant-garde. Le classicisme vient de son élaboration artisanale (sans conservateurs ni colorants), la nouveauté de l'ajout de l'orange."},{"id":"fr_FR","ocurrence":1,"type":"STRING","value":"Mélange parfait d'eau, de malt, de houblon et d'oranges de Valence issues de cultures propres à la marque Vendrell Gourmet. De couleur orangée un peu trouble, avec une mousse blanche et légère. Au nez l'arôme de céréale et les notes profondes d'agrumes apportées par l'orange dominent. En bouche elle se présente facilement avec un gaz très intégré et onctueux qui la rend veloutée. Tout converge vers une acidité équilibrée qui apporte de la fraîcheur en donnant un arrière-goût en bouche d'agrumes qui laisse réapparaître le fruit."}]}]},{"id":"GestionComprasStock","type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"Calificacion1","type":"STRING","value":"A"},{"id":"Calificacion2","type":"STRING","value":"A"},{"id":"Calificacion4","type":"STRING","value":"2A"},{"id":"Calificacion5","type":"STRING","value":"3A"},{"id":"TipoDeGestion","type":"STRING","value":"16"}]},{"id":"DimensionesYPeso","type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"UOM!Dimensiones!Unidad","type":"LOOKUP_TABLE","featureGroupID":"204","id_Ext":"347186090","value":"cm"},{"id":"UOM!PesoBruto!Unidad","type":"LOOKUP_TABLE","featureGrou